    "en": {
      "title": "Two more teams to Korea",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The signing of employment contracts in conjunction with the Korean employment program for Sri Lankan workers is currently ongoing.",
        "The signing of the surety bonds related to the jobs of 200 Korean employers took place today (22) at the Sri Lanka Foreign Employment Bureau Auditorium.",
        "Meanwhile, two other groups consisting of 131 people are scheduled to leave for work in South Korea on 26.07.2022 and 27.07.2022. This year, 3564 workers have gone to South Korea for work."
      ],
